      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      rf-zcp-des-cpv       to   w-tes-des-cpv (1)      .
           move      rf-zcp-cod-lng       to   w-tes-cod-lng (1)      .
           move      rf-zcp-tip-ord       to   w-tes-tip-ord (1)      .
           move      rf-zcp-alx-exp       to   w-tes-alx-exp (1)      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
