      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Codice lingua                       *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-cod-lng (1)    to   w-let-arc-zln-cod      .
           perform   let-arc-zln-000      thru let-arc-zln-999        .
           move      w-let-arc-zln-des    to   w-tes-cod-lng-des (1)  .
